CosmereResources.Def.MetalDef.label: duralumin
CosmereResources.Def.MetalDef.description: Duralumin is a lightweight yet remarkably strong alloy made by combining Aluminium with Copper. Its excellent strength-to-weight ratio makes it indispensable in advanced engineering and high-performance designs.
